extendedInfo.description: During the pregnancy time, a mother has to take the utmost care of her dressing because of the developments as well as the complications taking place in the body. The maternity wear clothes are made while keeping these things in mind. The maternity clothes are too comfortable to wear. It is always advised that the pregnancy wear should be made of soft fabrics like linen. It is because the linen made maternity dresses are quite easy to move about as well as to breathe. Besides, nowadays, a next maternity wear collection is also available which the pregnant women can carry in a stylish way.DISCLAIMER: The content provided in this app is collected using Feeds and Videos are hosted by YouTube and all are available in public domain. We have not uploaded any videos to YouTube. Apps are fetching the data from RSS feeds of different sites.This app provides an organized way to browse, read contents and watch YouTube Videos.
